properties.title: representative
properties.name: Pete Sessions
properties.biography: Sessions graduated from Southwestern University in 1978. After graduation, he began working for the Southwestern Bell Telephone company, which later became AT&T. Prior to his retirement to run for Congress in 1994, Sessions worked as a District Manager for AT&T.
